        "TileImage": "$($repository 0771273c-2ea6-4d2b-a636-409925f626c9).Image",
        "Description": "47, you&apos;re going to Miami, the &quot;Miami International&quot; race. Your targets are: Moses Lee and Adolph Rey.\r\r\rAdolph Rey is a cryptoinvestor. He wants to cheat the bookmaker by disqualifying Sierra Knox, so he disguises himself as a race marshal.\r\rMoses Lee is his partner in this deal. He will receive 25% of the money earned by Adolf.\r\rTry not to draw too much attention to yourself. Good luck, 47.",
